(Yanshosh can't play Striker, he's in stasis lock. What's he gonna 
do?)

Prebon/Ignatius

Prebon listened to Spears' comment. He thought about hitting Spears' 
for insubordination, but than realized she can't disobey him. He 
called to Ignatius.

"Ignatius, pick up that heap and carry him in your talons!"

"No problem boss!" Ignatius picked Striker up in his talons and 
carried Striker into the air. Prebon called to the group.

"Let's move out!"

Savage began to take his big steps and the others did their thing as 
The Trainers left their first battle, taking home two prizes.
